com.ep.ggs.system.nbt

Class CompoundTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ep.ggs.system.nbt.Tag<List<Tag<?>>>
      • com.ep.ggs.system.nbt.CompoundTag

  • public class CompoundTag
extends Tag<List<Tag<?>>>
    The Compound tag is used to store other tags. Every NBT file must begin with a compound tag. Its ID is 10.
